### Get my character (includes travel status)
GET {{host}}/characters/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step north
POST {{host}}/travel/move
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "north"
}

### Step south
POST {{host}}/travel/move
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "south"
}

### Step east
POST {{host}}/travel/move
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "east"
}

### Step west
POST {{host}}/travel/move
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "west"
}

### Travel to Thornhaven (50, 50)
POST {{host}}/travel/go
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 50,
  "y": 50
}

### Travel to a nearby coordinate (55, 50)
POST {{host}}/travel/go
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 55,
  "y": 50
}

### Travel across the map (76, 48) — The Greenwood
POST {{host}}/travel/go
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 76,
  "y": 48
}

### Check travel status
GET {{host}}/travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel active travel
POST {{host}}/travel/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to move into ocean (should fail 400)
POST {{host}}/travel/go
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 0,
  "y": 0
}
